                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220417-162-off844 t18220417-162-cd845"></join>, one handkerchief, value 4 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18220417-162-victim1541" type="victimName">
